{"tid":1384573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【728集會】示威者快速應對催淚彈　日本網民：香港年輕人好勇敢","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:42:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0bb472e67043e9cc569bc3d3da9e4c4fc7616b","tid":1384573,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"催涙ガスが警察側から飛んできたら、香港のデモ参加者は協力し、催涙ガス弾を速やかに処分する。長引いている抗議デモの中で磨いた技術。<a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/Q1fB8JUAcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FQ1fB8JUAcf&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=9d1f18bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/Q1fB8JUAcf</a><br />\n    &mdash; Martin Fackler (@martfack) July 29, 2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約時報《The New York Times》駐東京亞洲助理總編輯 Martin Fackler今早（29日）8時於Twitter分享上述片段（twitter@alexhofford），並以日文讚揚香港示威者迅速合作處理催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093174/org/e727fd8b457369bde658810c94779027.png/mooDyY4Xj_fF-VbWVpL1FC8DbPExupeT5ZZ31-WWd9c?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093174%2Forg%2Fe727fd8b457369bde658810c94779027.png%2FmooDyY4Xj_fF-VbWVpL1FC8DbPExupeT5ZZ31-WWd9c%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=c5328105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該帖文馬上被瘋傳，影片短短3小時已破百萬觀看次數，並登上Twitter日本熱門。<br />\n<br />\n有不少日本網民留言大讚示威者勇敢，日本也應該學習他們的應對技巧。亦有不少人感嘆示威者純熟的手法是香港動盪局勢逼成的。<br />\n<br />\n日本網民留言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093833/org/3d290476a88ae538ae4cb69745dd9d69.png/NdfvFLIMitdG2ZzQe16R7Y2MjYlZcTRCFlDICxZQyAs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093833%2Forg%2F3d290476a88ae538ae4cb69745dd9d69.png%2FNdfvFLIMitdG2ZzQe16R7Y2MjYlZcTRCFlDICxZQyAs&h=af77e7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093834/org/457f14f5094c8a32d6012196e65cac57.png/5NssWgSpcKpHLn2dm7Bm3j65kiaYPHxbKdrY3yna2N8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093834%2Forg%2F457f14f5094c8a32d6012196e65cac57.png%2F5NssWgSpcKpHLn2dm7Bm3j65kiaYPHxbKdrY3yna2N8&h=2076d5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093832/org/80d9dca9a591f1f5b46410a31eeb5d9f.png/YmazN-5F1x-Drn7Cs2OmK78OBrEeSYW_1fe9iNX3vYg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093832%2Forg%2F80d9dca9a591f1f5b46410a31eeb5d9f.png%2FYmazN-5F1x-Drn7Cs2OmK78OBrEeSYW_1fe9iNX3vYg&h=e4a3f4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093839/org/716c08d1a9e826f0064a866659c8d030.png/gniiwTveNU6m6LUCNhVVxzT3gXjo_rafIHDfISBw3yE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093839%2Forg%2F716c08d1a9e826f0064a866659c8d030.png%2FgniiwTveNU6m6LUCNhVVxzT3gXjo_rafIHDfISBw3yE&h=2a4552b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093835/org/d4e0950744cc677af5701c97190c3d7a.png/T2T2B4VI2UdcPFp0PSOjr2r_MyfDcp7N3CXl-9wl5fs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093835%2Forg%2Fd4e0950744cc677af5701c97190c3d7a.png%2FT2T2B4VI2UdcPFp0PSOjr2r_MyfDcp7N3CXl-9wl5fs&h=a571c048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093838/org/9b086fd91c67cb3810f206c3d303a73d.png/2x48lvLydTgoCsLbfoRLmrmMLT9fow_zfHTxwHx08cA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093838%2Forg%2F9b086fd91c67cb3810f206c3d303a73d.png%2F2x48lvLydTgoCsLbfoRLmrmMLT9fow_zfHTxwHx08cA&h=a3c02510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3093836/org/8cef3089cd87a08b1571df52b5c0d7fa.png/XO2Wwydq1Rm4q74FXpMS_GtybrOQXi3U44lLhuOJS4Y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3093836%2Forg%2F8cef3